Woodhaven Boulevard, west side north of Penelope Street, showing the Edward Tompkins house of 1852.  Nicholas Hasselberger owned it in 1873.  Other owners were J.J. Tompkins and J.T. Tompkins 1891 and 1896 respectively.

April 1923.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
